  <summary date="2021-02-04T20:16:47Z" status="Introduced in House">Great Lakes Water Protection Act

This bill restricts the diversion of waste streams into the Great Lakes from publicly owned wastewater treatment facilities. The bill also establishes the Great Lakes Green Infrastructure Grant Program to make grants to Great Lakes states to develop green infrastructure projects.</summary>
